### Login as admin -> stores accessToken into client global "adminToken"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Login as plain user -> stores accessToken into "userToken"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{user}}",
  "password": "{{userPass}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("userToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Create an order (ADMIN) -> stores order id into "orderId"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "c-1",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "p-1", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 9.99 },
    { "productId": "p-2", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 4.50 }
  ]
}

> {%
    client.global.set("orderId", response.body.order.id);
%}

### Get an order by id
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search orders (no filters, paged)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search orders by status
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders?status=CREATED&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Search orders by customer + date range
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders?customerId=c-1&createdFrom=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z&createdTo=2030-01-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Patch order status -> COMPLETED (ADMIN required)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Patch order status -> CANCELLED
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### Patch as USER -> expect 403 Forbidden
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Unauthenticated request -> expect 401
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders

### Actuator health (permitAll)
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
